68
00:05:19,028 --> 00:05:22,727
with the great actress, Ryo Haneki.

69
00:05:22,728 --> 00:05:24,327
Right, Conan?

70
00:05:24,328 --> 00:05:25,428
Yes.

71
00:05:28,528 --> 00:05:32,328
"Lake Nakajima."

72
00:05:38,128 --> 00:05:41,628
"Auberge Muto."

73
00:05:42,028 --> 00:05:44,827
