150
00:09:47,328 --> 00:09:48,728
-Cheers! -Cheers!

151
00:09:50,028 --> 00:09:53,027
They're both beautiful. As expected.

152
00:09:53,028 --> 00:09:55,327
True.

153
00:09:55,328 --> 00:09:58,427
You can't tell their like cats and dogs.

154
00:09:58,428 --> 00:10:00,427
They're actresses all right.

155
00:10:00,428 --> 00:10:01,727
Cut.

156
00:10:01,728 --> 00:10:03,127
Okay.

157
00:10:03,128 --> 00:10:05,027
Next, we're switching scenes!

158
00:10:05,028 --> 00:10:07,527
Aren't we going to retake the previous shot before that?

159
00:10:07,528 --> 00:10:10,027
Oh... I'm sorry...

160
00:10:10,028 --> 00:10:11,627
Talk about disorganized...

161
00:10:11,628 --> 00:10:13,827
I hope you don't keep me up all night for this.

162
00:10:13,828 --> 00:10:15,527
Because it's bad for my skin.

163
00:10:15,528 --> 00:10:16,627
That's right...

164
00:10:16,628 --> 00:10:19,928
Because Ryo's way past her prime.

165
00:10:23,528 --> 00:10:24,928
Let's retake the scene!

166
00:10:26,528 --> 00:10:28,527
Goodnight!

167
00:10:28,528 --> 00:10:31,327
After the breakfast shoot tomorrow,

168
00:10:31,328 --> 00:10:33,627
