169
00:10:33,628 --> 00:10:35,828
Thank you, everyone!

170
00:10:53,228 --> 00:10:55,828
I wonder who it is at this time of night?

171
00:11:02,528 --> 00:11:05,328
That's Ryo's room.

172
00:11:27,304 --> 00:11:28,804
