173
00:11:35,604 --> 00:11:36,703
This is...

174
00:11:36,704 --> 00:11:38,503
Kusumoto?

175
00:11:38,504 --> 00:11:39,904
Hey, hold it!

176
00:11:42,004 --> 00:11:43,703
No point running.

177
00:11:43,704 --> 00:11:45,904
I've already called the police.

178
00:11:47,104 --> 00:11:48,203
Don't tell me that...

179
00:11:48,204 --> 00:11:50,103
Is it about the transfer?

180
00:11:50,104 --> 00:11:52,703
Yeah! I want to stay at the set...

181
00:11:52,704 --> 00:11:55,603
But, I'll bet you told the higher ups to move me to desk work.

182
00:11:55,604 --> 00:11:59,203
