185
00:12:10,504 --> 00:12:12,003
No.

186
00:12:12,004 --> 00:12:13,603
What's the matter?

187
00:12:13,604 --> 00:12:14,903
Dad?

188
00:12:14,904 --> 00:12:18,303
Oh? Well...

189
00:12:18,304 --> 00:12:19,504
This is...

190
00:12:28,604 --> 00:12:32,803
-The wind is nice. -It feels great.

191
00:12:32,804 --> 00:12:36,103
I wonder if it'll be okay to keep shooting?

192
00:12:36,104 --> 00:12:39,703
After he said that, there are still a lot of people who don't like Ryo.

193
00:12:39,704 --> 00:12:42,603
That's why Pops and everyone else are keeping close watch over her

194
00:12:42,604 --> 00:12:44,204
